message.text:
In Japan, a new school semester/ business year starts in April. New friends/co-workers, new uniforms/suits...TONS of new things!
Every April, we are so much bloomed with dream and hope, like the full bloom of cherry blossoms!
How about the situation in your country:) ?When do you feel "fresh start"? 
新年よりも新しい気持ちになる日本の４月！あなたの国ではどうですか？
Japanese school expressions by scene! >> http://www.anime-manga.jp/Scene/School/

message.text:
#Hiragana Master
Say it Together! Basic Japanese Words in Japanese Alphabetical Order
Today's Word is "SA" SA KU RA　　#nihongo
日本の単語を五十音順にわかりやすく紹介！　「さ」くら

Sakura in Tokyo is in full bloom now, but will be gone within few days until next year...which makes it more beautiful!東京の桜は今が満開。でも来週には葉桜に。この儚さが桜の美しさを一層ひきたてます！
